name: Kenyatta WARNER, Petitioner v. COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania Rosalyn K. Robinson, (Judge for the Philadelphia Court of Common Pleas), Respondent

parties: Kenyatta WARNER, Petitioner v. COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania Rosalyn K. Robinson, (Judge for the Philadelphia Court of Common Pleas), Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 24th day of September, 2012, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the “Petition for Review (in the Nature of a Complaint in Mandamus)” is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
